        <li>Payment and renewal reminders</li>
        <li>Coverage changes or service notifications</li>
        <li>Follow-up messages related to inquiries or requests</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Message Frequency</h2>
    <p>
        Message frequency varies based on your account activity and communication needs.
    </p>

    <h2>Potential Fees for SMS Messaging</h2>
    <p>
        Message and data rates may apply. Fees depend on your mobile carrier and plan. Charges may vary for domestic or international messages.
    </p>

    <h2>Opt-In Method</h2>
    <p>
        Customers may opt in to receive SMS messages verbally during a phone call initiated through our website.
        During the call, customers are asked:
    </p>
    <p>
        “Do you agree to receive text messages from Chris Hunter Insurance Agency?
        Message frequency varies. Message and data rates may apply.
        Text HELP for help. Text STOP to opt out.
        View our privacy policy and terms on our website.”
    </p>
    <p>
        No SMS communication is initiated without customer consent.
    </p>

    <h2>Opt-Out</h2>
    <p>
        Customers may opt out of SMS messaging at any time by replying STOP to any received message.
        Once opted out, no further SMS messages will be sent.
        Customers may opt back in at any time by replying START.
    </p>

    <h2>Standard Messaging Disclosures</h2>
    <ul>
